PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1774530670
OL,3,CResidents concerned about financial
OL,4,Cburden of cladding crisis
OL,6,FIn response, the Ministry of Housing,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have never tried to claim
OL,8,Ffunds from the former residents of the
OL,9,FSpectrum building and have been clear
OL,10,Fthat they must be fairly compensated
OL,11,Ffor their losses."
